Sure! Here are some of the best colleges in the USA that provide professional training in Ukulele:

1. Berklee College of Music - Located in Boston, Massachusetts, Berklee College of Music offers a comprehensive program in Contemporary Writing and Production, which includes courses in Ukulele performance and technique. [Visit Berklee College of Music](https://www.berklee.edu/){:target="_blank"}

2. University of Southern California (USC) - The Thornton School of Music at USC offers a Bachelor of Music in Popular Music Performance, where students can specialize in Ukulele. [Visit USC Thornton School of Music](https://music.usc.edu/){:target="_blank"}

3. University of Miami - The Frost School of Music at the University of Miami offers a Bachelor of Music in Studio Music and Jazz, which includes courses in Ukulele performance and improvisation. [Visit University of Miami Frost School of Music](https://www.miami.edu/frost/){:target="_blank"}

4. University of North Texas - The College of Music at the University of North Texas offers a Bachelor of Music in Jazz Studies, where students can focus on Ukulele as their primary instrument. [Visit University of North Texas College of Music](https://music.unt.edu/){:target="_blank"}

5. California Institute of the Arts (CalArts) - CalArts offers a Bachelor of Fine Arts in Music with a focus on World Music Performance, which includes opportunities to study and perform on the Ukulele. [Visit California Institute of the Arts](https://music.calarts.edu/){:target="_blank"}

6. University of Hawaii at Manoa - Located in Honolulu, Hawaii, the University of Hawaii at Manoa offers a Bachelor of Music in Performance with a specialization in Ukulele. This program provides a unique opportunity to study the Ukulele in its cultural and historical context. [Visit University of Hawaii at Manoa](https://manoa.hawaii.edu/music/){:target="_blank"}

Please note that admission requirements and program offerings may vary for each college. It is recommended to visit their respective websites for more detailed information about the Ukulele programs they offer.
